Rafael Nadal Beats David Ferrer for Seventh Consecutive Monte Carlo Title

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-04-17T14:50:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-17/rafael-nadal-beats-david-ferrer-for-seventh-consecutive-monte-carlo-title.html
World No. 1 Rafael Nadal clinched a
record seventh straight Monte Carlo tennis title with a 6-4, 7-5
win over fellow Spaniard  David Ferrer  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
